      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Christophe Théron</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:195px;\"><a href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/chesstiger/us.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1/1c/Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"265\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Christophe Théron <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Christophe Théron</b>,<br />\na French computer chess programmer living in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guadeloupe\">Guadeloupe</a>. He started chess programming at the age of 17 in 1982 on a <a href=\"/TRS-80\" title=\"TRS-80\">TRS-80</a> 1.77 Mhz home computer <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Christophe is author of the chess engine <a href=\"/Chess_Tiger\" title=\"Chess Tiger\">Chess Tiger</a>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=13569\">Self-test and others rating stuffs...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=14017\">Re: Square-of-the-pawn</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 13, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Blitz\" title=\"Blitz\">Blitz</a>, <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=16142\">Chess Tiger on LCT2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 26, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/LCT_II\" title=\"LCT II\">LCT II</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=72642\">Chess Tiger 12.0 wins the FCCC together with Capture</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 10, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/FCCC_1999\" title=\"FCCC 1999\">FCCC 1999</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=114377\">Re: Question:1.hashtable 2.board 3.C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 13, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a>, <a href=\"/10x12_Board\" title=\"10x12 Board\">10x12 Board</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=114438\">0x88 is not so smart</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCC</a>, June 13, 2000 </dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=114558\">Re: Question:1.hashtable 2.board 3.C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Vector_Attacks\" title=\"Vector Attacks\">Vector Attacks</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=174569\">Report on Massy 2001</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Massy_2001\" title=\"Massy 2001\">Massy 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=274566\">[half OT</a> Need help: choice of an IDE to build Chess Tiger for Linux] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=297371\">PalmOS devices are as powerful as PocketPC devices</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 20, 2003</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13145\">Chess Tiger 2007.1 has just been released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23037\">To Jeroen and interested minds, re. Tiger node count</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 15, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nodes_per_second&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nodes per second (page does not exist)\">Nodes per second</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23252\">A very simple question to Vas that can end it all</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 25, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23386\">How a court detects a derivative work</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 30, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23442\">On escaping copyright by rewriting everything</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2008</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=350101&amp;t=34402\">Re: DeepTiger</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 21, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39015\">Help: I need testers for the iOS version of Chess Tiger</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39178\">Chess Tiger for iOS has been updated</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Christophe Théron</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 25, 2011</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=14\">Christophe Théron's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstiger.com/index.html\">Chess Tiger: the best chess program for iOS (iPhone, iPod touch and iPad)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/chesstiger/us.html\">Chess Tiger - About us</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christophe_Th%C3%A9ron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/chesstiger/us.html\">Chess Tiger - About us</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/authors.htm\">Meet the Authors</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301134609\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 59/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 114/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2